Test case 21: Calculate cost for 3 hours of Long-Term Surface Parking (North Lot).
  - User story: As a customer, I want to know the cost of parking for 3 hours in the Long-Term Surface Parking (North Lot).
  - Input:
        Parking Lot: Long-Term Surface Parking (North Lot)
        Entry Date and Time: 04/01/2023 2:00 PM
        Leaving Date and Time: 04/01/2023 5:00 PM
    Expected output:
        Total Cost: $6.00

